data.description: This home has NO HOA, is being sold AS IS and qualifies for 100% USDA financing. It's a 2 bed/2 bath ranch home on a full, partially finished, basement. It just needs you, your imagination and some TLC to make this the perfect starter home or investment property. There's definitely room to grow in this home with the additional living space, two additional rooms and a full bathroom in the basement. This home is centrally located to Cumming, Dawsonville, and Gainesville. Nearby you'll find several boat ramps for access to Lake Lanier, there's so many restaurants and lots of options for your shopping needs. The North Georgia Premium Outlets are under 15 minutes away and in 30 minutes or less, you can get to Downtown Dawsonville, the new City Center in Cumming, Historic Downtown Dahlonega, and the Gainesville Square. This home is also in the highly sought after Forsyth County school district. Schedule your showing today.
